user.biography: We are Mebie Baby! We offer modern + simple designed Swaddle Blankets and Baby basics.  collabs@mebiebaby.com #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 31, 2021. May be an image of baby.

node.text: How cute are the vanilla footie and the cream quilt together? 😍 #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 30, 2021.

node.text: Such a cute little set! We love the oversized size of the burp cloths. Great for spit up, messes and even changing your baby laying on one! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 29, 2021 tagging @piccalio. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text: How cute is this? We love that the sizes 6-12 and up in footies now have grips! Your babe can scoot and run around in these without slipping. 👏 #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 26, 2021 tagging @minabaie, and @papperapparel. May be an image of text that says 'GIVEAWAY'.

node.text:
G I V E A W A Y winner @paigee.reinhart
We have teamed up with two of our favorite brands @minabaie + @papperapparel to gift you the ultimate mom and baby bundle!
We are gifting $100 from @mebie.baby • $100 from @papperapparel • $100 from @minabaie

All you need to do is like and save this post, be sure to follow all 3 shops, tag your friends in separate comments and share in your stories for bonus entries.

Must be 18+ to enter, shipping fees may apply. Not endorsed or sponsored by Instagram. 
**Please be aware of spam accounts! We never ask for any type of personal information for a gifting!**

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 26, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.

node.text: This short set is so adorable! Our next print order will come with more rainbow footies and gowns, I know some of you didn’t grab them before they sold out! #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 24, 2021.

node.text: We love putting together cute gift ideas or take home outfits. This is perfect for a gender neutral gift! Did you find out the gender before birth or did you wait? #mebiebaby

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Baby Swaddles + Basics! 🌿 on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, baby and indoor.

node.text: When we started making the organic footies we just had them in three sizes. We now have them in newborn up to 3T and I love that babies and toddlers can enjoy them. Do you put your toddlers in footies? #mebiebaby
